_sText:
Feels like you've been here before, but you are not sure. You see a silhouette of something in the distant fog. You feel tired. Maybe it's best you move forward instead of staying put. Maybe this will be the final one.

The map contains a mixture of bunnyhop and kz. You should reserve an hour or more to beat it. For those who are extra bored, you can try hard mode (bonus 1) which has no checkpoints. It's not fair, but that's why it's a bonus.

Start and end zones (main & bonus) are marked with triggers (mod_zone_start & mod_zone_end).
